      <title>特朗普团队寻求放宽美国自动驾驶汽车规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/trump-team-seeking-to-ease-rules-for-self-driving-cars-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的过渡团队成员告诉顾问，他们计划将自动驾驶汽车的联邦框架作为交通部的优先事项之一。彭博社的 David Welch 报道了这一消息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/trump-team-seeking-to-ease-rules-for-self-driving-cars-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 21:50:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
